title: Video: Admiral Radley (Grandaddy & Earlimart)
description: See the band, featuring members of Grandaddy and Earlimart, perform three new songs from its upcoming album, 'I Heart California.' This video was shot by NPR Music at the historic Driskill Hotel in Austin, TX at the 2010 SXSW festival and conference.
